I've sent 11-3 to pick you up.

47
00:04:56,041 --> 00:04:59,083
We're investigating the
kidnapping of a little girl.

48
00:04:59,166 --> 00:05:03,166
We have reason to believe a
Hekatoncheires may be involved.

49
00:05:05,500 --> 00:05:08,125
How long are you
going to stay at Hitomi's?

50
